targets.expr:
$interval $__interval / 10 / 'BUCKET_COUNT' STORE
$interval $BUCKET_COUNT / 'BUCKET_SIZE' STORE


'renameWithMultipleLabelValues@1.0.0' FIMPORT
'grafanaMultiVariable@1.0.1' FIMPORT
'transformToGrafanaTable@1.0.0' FIMPORT


$nodes @grafanaMultiVariable 'All' '~.*' REPLACE 'nodes' STORE

[ 
  $token 
  'os.uptime' 
  { 'host' $nodes }
  $end $interval $BUCKET_SIZE 2 * +
]
FETCH 

[ SWAP bucketizer.last $end $BUCKET_SIZE 1 ] BUCKETIZE

SORT

<%
  DROP
  DUP LABELS 'host' GET 'node' STORE
  { 'node' $node } RELABEL
%> LMAP 

[ 'node' ] 'A' @transformToGrafanaTable
